Package: mktinsight
Type: Package
Title: Tool for Contextual Analysis of Email Subjects
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Ben Ziomek 
Maintainer: Ben Ziomek <bziomek@chicagobooth.edu>
URL: https://github.com/bziomek/mktinsight
BugReports: https://github.com/bziomek/mktinsight/issues
Description: Leverages spacy and quanteda to analyze sent email data.
    Distinguishes between senior and junior contacts by job title,
    and produces a table of words and sentence structures that 
    correlated with successful email opens, along with the odds ratio
    that an email is opened given it contains the stated structure.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    quanteda,
    spacyr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
